        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Border Agents Stay Employed Act or the BASE Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits using federal funds to require any U.S. Customs and Border Protection officer or employee to receive a COVID-19 vaccine.</p>]]>
        </text>
